Listerine Total Care Zero provides the same six dental hygiene benefits in one as Listerine Total Care Fluoride Anticavity Mouthwash, but in a less intense, alcohol-free mouthwash formula. With up to 2.4x the fluoride uptake than Act mouthwash brand**, this daily fluoride oral rinse formula helps prevent dental cavities by providing 50% greater strengthening of weakened enamel vs. brushing alone*. It freshens breath, kills 99% of germs that cause bad breath, cleans your whole mouth. From the #1 dentist-recommended brand of over the counter mouthwashes, this mouthwash for bad breath in Fresh Mint flavor gives your mouth a clean feeling you can taste, all with a zero alcohol formula. *In laboratory studies **In laboratory tests compared to Act Anticavity Fluoride Mouthwash, Act Total Care Anticavity Fluoride Mouthwash.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Contains sodium laurel sulphate
reviews.reviewText: I bought after reading so many positive reviews, some even saying it helps with canker sores. Sodium laurel sulphate has been shown to cause canker sores. Within days of using this for one single canker sore, my tongue has broken out with them and is in so much pain. I’ve stopped using it and am now rinsing with warm saltwater only which seems to be helping. This mouthwash was the only change in my oral hygiene as of late.
Simplemente me encanta! No arde ya que no tiene alcohol; deja la boca super limpia y fresca. De los enjuagues listerine, es el que más me gusta. Recomendadisimo!
